729611f-a.title: Richmond: Sand Lane - Oceanside Avenue
729611f-a.text:
Sand Lane, east side, near Oceanside Avenue (at
the railroad tracks), showing a bungalow colony at South
Beach.
June 2, 1935
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

729610f-a.title: Richmond: Sand Lane - Oceanside Avenue
729610f-a.text:
Sand Lane, south from Oceanside Avenue (at the
railroad tracks) to Seaside Boulevard. Shown is the business
oenter and bath houses of South Beach.
June 2, 1935
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
